    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You aptly command your Pod to focus its efforts toward scanning and examining the enemy, searching for their openings and weak points. Once per round, you can cast this jutsu to have your Pod perform a <strong>Defensive Scan</strong> or an <strong>Offensive Scan</strong>, granting one of the listed effects below depending on your choice:</p><hr /><h3><strong>Defensive Scan:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Your Pod performs the <strong>Read the Enemy</strong> skill-based action when a creature would take any action, requiring no action cost and no components to trigger. In place of a skill check, it rolls 1d20 + half your character level + your proficiency bonus. On a success, you are immediately informed of the details of the action, and all allied creatures within 30 feet of you that can hear you gain the benefits of a success.</p></li></ul><hr /><h3><strong>Offensive Scan:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Your Pod rolls 1d20 + half your character level + your proficiency bonus and compares the result to the passive Deception of a creature within 120 feet of you. On a success, all allied creatures within 30 feet of you that can hear you gain a +1d4 bonus to their next attack roll against the targeted creature.</p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and gain a +2 bonus to the roll.</p>",
